race.comment: MR SQUARE PANTS (6) is yet to break through after seven career starts. Managed to find the placings at Port Macquarie two starts back before finishing ninth over 1509m at Port Macquarie last time. Won't get too many better chances to open his account. CASSINI (4) met with solid support last start over 1400m at Inverell when second, beaten 5.5 lengths. Great chance to atone. MISS MIDAS TOUCH (2) finished 4 lengths away in fifth at her last appearance over 1210m at Lismore on October 19 after she got a long way back in the run. Finds the right race and is worth consideration. Looking for big improvement from ADEEL IT'S A STEAL (1) from the inside draw second up.
